phi1 <- 0.8
theta1 <- 0.4
sigma <- 2
model <- list(ar = phi1,ma = theta1)
arma11 <- arima.sim(model=model,n = 200,innov=rnorm(200,0,sd=sigma))
matplot(arma11,lwd=2,type="l",col="blue",main="Simulated Time Series")

ml1 <- arima(arma11,order = c(1,0,1),method="ML")
